# SPCTOM
Implementation of **SPCTOM: Smooth Path-Constrained Time-Optimal Motion** trajectory planning.  
Course Project **EE6412: Optimal Control**.  
Inspired from reference paper: _Smooth and Time-Optimal Trajectory Planning for Industrial Manipulators along Specified Paths - D. Constantinescu, E. A. Croft_
